quran[19{c,v,t}:
38,43,Wa wahabnaa lahoo ahlahoo wa mislahum ma'ahum rahmatam minna wa zikraa li ulil albaab
38,44,"Wa khuz biyadika dighsan fadrib bihee wa laa tahnas, innaa wajadnaahu saabiraa; ni'mal 'abd; innahooo awwaab"
38,45,Wazkur 'ibaadanaaa Ibraaheema wa Is-haaqa wa Ya'qooba ulil-aydee walabsaar
38,46,Innaaa akhlasnaahum bi khaalisatin zikrad daar
38,47,Wa innahum 'indanaa laminal mustafainal akhyaar
38,48,Wazkur Ismaa'eela wal Yasa'a wa Zal-Kifli wa kullum minal akhyaar
38,49,Haazaa zikr; wa inna lilmuttaqeena lahusna ma aab
38,50,Jannaati 'adnim mufat tahatal lahumul abwaab
38,51,Muttaki'eena feehaa yad'oona feehaa bifaakihatin kaseeratinw wa sharaab
38,52,Wa 'indahum qaasiraatut tarfi atraab
38,53,Haaza maa too'odoona li Yawmil Hisaab
38,54,Inna haazaa larizqunaa maa lahoo min nafaad
38,55,Haazaa; wa inna littaagheena lasharra ma-aab
38,56,Jahannama yaslawnahaa fai'sal mihaad
38,57,Haazaa falyazooqoohu hameemunw wa ghassaaq
38,58,Wa aakharu min shak liheee azwaaj
38,59,Haazaa fawjum muqtahimum ma'akum laa marhabam bihim; innahum saalun Naar
38,60,Qaaloo bal antum laa marhabam bikum; antum qaddamtumoohu lanaa fabi'sal qaraar
38,61,Qaaloo Rabbanaa man qaddama lanaa haaza fazidhu 'azaaban di'fan fin Naar
